Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?\NNo need to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair clip is crooked.\NI'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NYou look very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert who fled to\Nthe West a few days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared before the press\Nwith his wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Liebert\Ndid not appear to be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And their twin son and daughter\Nare both wearing bright expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert, what do you\Nthink of West Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When I realize that I'm free to say whatever\NI want, I'm unable to find any words.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the answer to that question is in\Nthe smiling faces of my wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your children also seem\Nto be enjoying their freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, would you care to talk\Nabout the current situation in the East?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which hand is it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's yours Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, an acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more.\NWhich hand is it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct again.\NHere, it's yours again Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, open up\Nboth of your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Either one\Nwould have been correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All the acorns here\Nare yours anyway Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey brother, did you see\Nthe town on the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely different\Nfrom the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots\Nof pretty shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There were also\Nlots of clothes and toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw them too,\Nright, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's yours too, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you on TV, Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother... Is somebody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother... Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How Mr. Josef\Nand Mrs. Ciara died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How Mr. Bedger died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Today. ..the monster came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed all of them,\Ndidn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster came\Nto take us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After you shoot me, wipe the gun with\Na cloth and throw it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to shoot me\Nin the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After you shoot me,\Nrun away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away so the monster\Ncan't catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Even if I die,\Nyou are me and I am you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That night... That rainy night.. .\NSomeone came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone came\Nto that mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?! Who came?! Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The monster came.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was the house on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No one lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They are saying it was arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come with us\Nfor a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf\Nwants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,General.. .Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. ..Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were called upon too,\Nweren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan wrote a letter to me saying that\Nhe'd be waiting at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was just barely able\Nto get to Prague hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've received\Nthat letter, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is now the only person who\Nsends letters to the man called Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born into a military family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was promised a life as one of the\Nchosen ones since the time I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But now. .. The one who knows me\Nas I know myself is that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the Red Rose Mansion\Nburned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably revealing\Nthemselves right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those whose names\Nwere taken, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to determine\Nwhere the fire started?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It seems it was a hall\Non the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,From the concentrated flames in that\Narea, it was probably kerosene or gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure unless\Nwe investigate carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are signs that a wall\Nin the hallway was broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come here a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I dug it up when I saw something\Nat the base of the rose bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They just keep coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll reveal themselves\Nafter many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one knows\Ntheir names any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only clue to find Tenma.\NAt this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way.\NLet us through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Contact headquarters!\NThis is an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeletons!\NTons of human remains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,46?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1981 , 46 people suddenly\Nvanished in that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was among the intelligence\NI had received in East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They were doing an experiment\Nat that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Move back, move back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn away any onlookers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children were\Nprobably born there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother... I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't walk anymore.\NI'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.. .\NAre we going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother... Say my name.\NSay my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Say my name. My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And some water to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Because Johan was\Nsuch a wonderful name."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children had no names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I gave that child the name\NJohan, something awakened inside of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No. There's no point in\Ntalking about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I no longer have\Na tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough,\NGeneral Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann is. ..\Nwith people from my organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us formed\Nour organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Professor Geidlitz,\Nwho was killed, and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva.. .is with the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to use Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They mustn't come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I live or not,\NI can no longer stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to go wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop him. Save us, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Helmut...\NHelmut Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no longer anyone\Nwho knows me as Helmut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me. ..by my name.\NIt's the proof of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut.. .\NYou're Helmut Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what Johan saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A world without names...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It burned down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate is locked.\NThe police probably made it off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lipsky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how important\Nthis place was to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to the recitals here\Nwhen you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina. .. It should have been\Nan important place for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This might have been the place that\Ncould have brought back your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people piled up dead in\Na large hall in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The vision you had was true.\NI was surprised when I saw the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that they found the remains\Nof 46 people at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it as your brother...\Nas Johan said it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What did my brother. ..\NJohan see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something terribly frightening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,True fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been there at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were there,\Nwould I have become the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... It might have been a good\Nthing for this place to burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that it would\Nbe more painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I couldn't live\Nif I lost this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just don't feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is just\Nfull of sad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't a superior pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't meet his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If...If I had been able\Nto meet his expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I became unwanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lipsky what about\Nyour mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. .I've never lived with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If your memory comes back Nina,\NI hope they are fun memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...fun memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what fun memories are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any fun memories,\Nyou just have to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma said that we should\Njust start making them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, you've got ketchup\Naround your mouth. It's all red.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:19:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making a new puppet play\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's ever wanted\Nto watch my puppet plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But people might like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your new work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a girl who's\Nlost her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream that I was\Nbeing chased by a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream that I was\Nchasing a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to dance too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday,\NI'll have a wonderful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday,\Nthat dream will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out\Nwhat comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make this girl's story\Nhave a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still can't think of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make it\Na happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make it\Na happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl made up her mind\Nto go on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what\Nkind of journey it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what\Nis waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But the girl will courageously\Ncontinue her journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl turns and waves her hand\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To search for\Na happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you've come bâ€“
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you,\NMr. Lipsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the owner of\Nthe Red Rose Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta's son,\Naren't you?
